<div class="thumb tright"><div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Quovadis-scenenewspaper-1915.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a2/Quovadis-scenenewspaper-1915.jpg/220px-Quovadis-scenenewspaper-1915.jpg" width="220" height="188" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a2/Quovadis-scenenewspaper-1915.jpg/330px-Quovadis-scenenewspaper-1915.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a2/Quovadis-scenenewspaper-1915.jpg/440px-Quovadis-scenenewspaper-1915.jpg 2x" data-file-width="1933" data-file-height="1648" /></a>  <div class="thumbcaption"><div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Quovadis-scenenewspaper-1915.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>Film still</div></div></div>
