<li><a href="/wiki/Quo_Vadis_(1951_film)" title="Quo Vadis (1951 film)">1951 film</a> directed by <a href="/wiki/Mervyn_LeRoy" title="Mervyn LeRoy">Mervyn LeRoy</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Quo_Vadis%3F_(miniseries)" title="Quo Vadis? (miniseries)">1985 TV mini-series</a> directed by <a href="/wiki/Franco_Rossi_(director)" title="Franco Rossi (director)">Franco Rossi</a></li>
